headline.main: Alphabet Lawsuit Against Uber Cements End of Uneasy Marriage
headline.print_headline: Alphabet Lawsuit Against Uber Cements End of Uneasy Marriage

lead_paragraph: When Uber Technologies Inc [UBER.UL] was raising venture capital in 2013, it was one of the hottest deals around – and no one was more eager to write a check than Bill Maris and David Krane of Google's venture capital arm.
